<p>
  <span class="nym">Nivo</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">A hypocoristic of any of various names beginning with <span class="lang">Gothic</span> <i>niujis</i>, <span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>niuwi, niwi</i> 'new'.
</span>
  
</p>
  
  
  


